title: 01041 Nand replacement
message: This board had 6 nands but when trying to reball 2 of my donor Nands were damaged. From Iboff's video it appears I can still transfer the remaining 4 but I need to cutoff 3v3 for ocarina on the two FLP's to make them NFLP's. Would removing R5610 be the easiest way to cutoff the U9100/9200?

title: 01041 Nand replacement
message: Turns out it was R5610 in my case to remove both port 1 side nands
